					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Oh, don't forget! If you want it to work on the real NES, you must have your reset, nmi, and irq routines in $C000-$FFFF! Do not put it in $8000-$BFFF, otherwise it won't play. It will play on an emulator, but not on the real hardware. I think that's correct. I think I heard that in the "Bank Switching" forum.</div>

					
